'''湯姆·卡瓦納夫'''（'''Thomas Patrick "Tom" Cavanagh'''，{{bd|1963年|10月26日}}）是加拿大的一位演員。他出演過眾多美國電視劇。卡瓦納夫是出生在渥太華的一個愛爾蘭裔的天主教家庭<ref name=rothstein>{{cite news|url=http://www.journalgazette.net/article/20090713/BLOGS02/907129922|title=Fame And Notre Dame: Actor Tom Cavanagh|work=[[The_Journal_Gazette|The Journal Gazette]]|location=[[Fort_Wayne,_Indiana|Fort Wayne, Indiana]]|date=July 13, 2009|quote=That was the start of it, so to speak, and we're Irish Catholic and Notre Dame, well, they're the Irish...|accessdate=2014-08-13|first=Michael|last=Rothstein|archive-date=2014-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141013203832/http://www.journalgazette.net/article/20090713/BLOGS02/907129922|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 著名作品包括於《[[閃電俠_(2014年電視影集)|閃電俠]]》飾演哈里森‧威爾斯博士。並於部分集數擔任導演。

==簡介==
2014年起，Cavanagh一直參與[[CW電視台|CW電視台]]影集《[[閃電俠_(2014年電視影集)|閃電俠]]》主演，扮演了Harrison Wells博士的各分身<ref name="tvg">{{cite news|title=Ed's Tom Cavanagh Joins The CW's The Flash Pilot|url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/Flash-CW-Tom-Cavanagh-1077515.aspx|last=Abrams|first=Natalie|date=February 10, 2014|work=[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]]|accessdate=2014-08-13|archive-date=2014-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814033249/http://www.tvguide.com/News/Flash-CW-Tom-Cavanagh-1077515.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一季中扮演[[Eobard_Thawne|Eobard Thawne]] / [[Reverse-Flash|Reverse-Flash]]，同時在第一季中扮演Earth-1的Wells，也在CW的[[超級英雄搏擊俱樂部|超級英雄搏擊俱樂部]]宣傳片中扮演這個角色<ref>{{cite news|url=http://screenrant.com/flash-arrow-tv-fight-club-promo-video/|title='The Flash' & 'Arrow' Stars Battle in 'Superhero Fight Club' Promo|date=April 13, 2015|accessdate=2017-05-15|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428115209/http://screenrant.com/flash-arrow-tv-fight-club-promo-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這個角色在2017年的四部劇集的交叉活動“地球上的危機-X”中再次出場<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://screenrant.com/arrowverse-crisis-earth-x-dark-flash-origin/|title=Crisis On Earth-X Reveals Dark Flash's Origin|last=Leane|first=Rob|date=November 28, 2017|work=Screen Rant|access-date=2018-04-27|archive-date=2018-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180420183050/https://screenrant.com/arrowverse-crisis-earth-x-dark-flash-origin/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第二季扮演地球-2的“哈利”威爾斯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/flash-finale-spoilers-eddie-thawne-796679|title='The Flash' EP on "Heartbreaking" Finale Death, Season 2 Speedsters and Villains|date=May 19, 2015|accessdate=2015-09-23|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924153049/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/flash-finale-spoilers-eddie-thawne-796679|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第三季的地球19的HR<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cultfix.co.uk/the-flash-314-attack-on-central-city-review-32062.htm|title=The Flash: 314 "Attack on Central City" Review – Cult Fix|publisher=Cultfix.co.uk|date=2017-03-02|accessdate=2017-12-15|archive-date=2018-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619193219/http://cultfix.co.uk/the-flash-314-attack-on-central-city-review-32062.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同樣在第三季中，他演奏了另外三個doppelgängers（來自地球-17的蒸汽朋克風格，英國口音的分身，來自未命名的地球的鄉巴佬和來自另一個未命名的地球的講法語的啞劇演員），作為浮雕，他在第三季“The Once and Future Flash”中的導演處女作<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://screenrant.com/the-flash-the-once-and-future-flash-review-barry-time-travel-savitar/|title=The Flash: The Once And Future Flash Review & Discussion|date=April 25, 2017|work=Screen Rant|access-date=2017-08-14|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170813132516/http://screenrant.com/the-flash-the-once-and-future-flash-review-barry-time-travel-savitar/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第四季中，Cavanagh以地球2的哈利出場，另外扮演其他六個版本的Wells：地球12的Harrison Wolfgang Wells，地-47的H. Lothario Wells，地球22的半人/半機Wells 2.0，來自地球13的魔法師，地球-24和惠普的桑尼威爾斯地球25。第五季，Cavanagh出現在偵探Sherloque Wells身上<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://ew.com/recap/the-flash-season-5-episode-3/|title=The Flash recap: Sherloque Wells helps reveal Nora and Cicada's connection|last=Agard|first=Chancellor|date=October 23, 2018|work=EW|access-date=December 7, 2018|archive-date=2018-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181119134048/https://ew.com/recap/the-flash-season-5-episode-3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並執導第100集。

